Class DDisjunctionArray<D extends DObject>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DArrayView<DDisjunction<D>>, DFieldView<DDisjunction<D>>

    public class DDisjunctionArray<D extends DObject>
extends DArray<DDisjunction<D>>
    A DDisjunction-valued array bound to the same slot as a specific DObject-valued "source" array, enabling the setting of disjunction values for the slot.

    NOTE: Objects of this type can only be created for source-arrays whose associated slots are abstract-editable (i.e. have editabilily status of IEditability.FULL).
